{"tid":1070220,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係點樣去愛一個人？","createTime":"2019-03-20T13:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T14:22:13.000Z","uid":135837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9694dba8c1cdaca6accda323d7426ee0efb8c1","tid":1070220,"uid":135837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"最初未一齊講到你幾好，點樣好過曬佢之前啲ex<br />\n一齊之後幾個月又嫌你喱樣嫌你嗰樣，同你講其實咁樣都係為你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算佢點發我脾氣都好都會死死氣做氹佢嗰個，因為唔想冇咗個男朋友！但又自己會覺得好似變到唔再係自己咁<br />\n就算性格大家有幾似，價值觀諗嘢根本就唔同<br />\n其實好想維持新鮮感，唔想咁快分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baaf0540c3bc4f7d59343b5fe2d0d1609640d2d0","tid":1070220,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84289c25d7806e410081d466495a2db1b31d1a5","tid":1070220,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}